  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Shuck the corn and remove any silk or debris.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the almond flour, ground cumin, smoked paprika, and melted chocolate.",
    "Rub the mixture evenly onto the corn, making sure to coat all surfaces.",
    "Grill the corn for 10-12 minutes, turning every 2-3 minutes, until slightly charred and tender.",
    "While the corn is grilling, melt the lard or shortening in a small saucepan over low heat.",
    "Add the mayonnaise to the melted lard or shortening and stir to combine.",
    "Once the corn is done, brush the mayonnaise mixture evenly onto each ear of corn.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped cilantro and a squeeze of lime juice."
  ],
